      "updated": 1774806043
    },
    {
      "id": "69c96b770000000000a6d7c9",
      "text": "[2026-03-29 Mijjiko] -> 2026-03-30 Mijikko -> [Next-Day Mijikko]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774807928,
      "updated": 1774886398
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964170000000000fc2147",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806040,
      "updated": 1774806040
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964200000000000fc2148",
      "text": "[[日記]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806049,
      "updated": 1774806054
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964200000000000fc2149",
      "text": "\t[新型のAnker Nano Chargerがとても良さげ]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806049,
      "updated": 1774806254
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9ed920000000000f1236d",
      "text": "\t換気扇や加湿器の音がやたらと耳に響く",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841234,
      "updated": 1774841252
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9eda40000000000f1236e",
      "text": "\t\t多分[水分不足]だなこれ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841252,
      "updated": 1774841262
    },
    {
      "id": "69c9edb00000000000f1236f",
      "text": "\t\t#自分の体調不良を感じる瞬間",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774841263,
      "updated": 1774841305
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1be6000000000060cf49",
      "text": "\tVRChatやVRの設定見直したらだいぶ軽くなった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853095,
      "updated": 1774853668
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1bf1000000000060cf4a",
      "text": "\t\tグラフィック 高 → 中に変更",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853105,
      "updated": 1774853120
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1bff000000000060cf4b",
      "text": "\t\t[PICO Connect]の解像度設定 標準画質 → 超高画質に変更",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853120,
      "updated": 1774853185
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1c41000000000060cf4c",
      "text": "\t\tSteamのVRChatのレンダリング解像度設定 100% (4K) → 66%",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853185,
      "updated": 1774853212
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1c63000000000060cf4d",
      "text": "\t\t\t[XSOverLay]の画質を上げたかった",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853220,
      "updated": 1774853247
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1c7f000000000060cf4e",
      "text": "\t\t\tちょっと見やすくなったかも程度だけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853247,
      "updated": 1774853256
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1e19000000000060cf4f",
      "text": "\t\t[XSOverLay]で湾曲したオーバーレイの設定を有効化",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853658,
      "updated": 1774853748
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca1e73000000000060cf50",
      "text": "\t\t\t表示面積がちょっと増える",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774853748,
      "updated": 1774853758
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca6c330000000000e05dfb",
      "text": "\tなんか[問題解決]の際に[原因の切り分け]するのがすっかり癖になってしまっているな",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774873652,
      "updated": 1774873676
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca6c1e0000000000e05df9",
      "text": " \t仕事のせいなのか元々そういう性格だったのかはわからないけど",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774873630,
      "updated": 1774873652
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca6c600000000000e05dfc",
      "text": " \tスコープを絞ったほうが楽ということに気づいているので、会社のせいということにしておこう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774873697,
      "updated": 1774873720
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca7c910000000000c09bfe",
      "text": " [FUJIYAMA]って時計と人数カウンターあったんだ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774877842,
      "updated": 1774877843
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca7c920000000000c09bff",
      "text": " \t初めて知った",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774877843,
      "updated": 1774877845
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964290000000000fc214c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806058,
      "updated": 1774806058
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964260000000000fc214a",
      "text": "[[タスク]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806054,
      "updated": 1774806056
    },
    {
      "id": "69c964260000000000fc214b",
      "text": "\t✅マイク買う",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774806055,
      "updated": 1774809664
    },
    {
      "id": "69c972350000000000f12366",
      "text": "\t\t買った",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774809654,
      "updated": 1774809656
    },
    {
      "id": "69c972450000000000f12367",
      "text": "\t\t[MV7+]にした",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774809670,
      "updated": 1774809676
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca67be0000000000e05df5",
      "text": "\t\t✅届いてセットアップまでした",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774872510,
      "updated": 1774877852
    },
    {
      "id": "69c972720000000000f12368",
      "text": "\t就活",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774809715,
      "updated": 1774809717
    },
    {
      "id": "69ca6be20000000000e05df8",
      "text": "\t\t[職務経歴書]書く",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774873570,
      "updated": 1774873576
    },
